In re Resignation of Gross.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Gross (1995), 72 Ohio St.3d 1215.]

(No. 95-1028 Submitted June 7, 1995 Decided June 8, 1995.)

The resignation as an attorney of Alden Edgar Gross III of Toledo, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0006253, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
